<figureCitation id="1BE0CBEFCC0F3F67A2A99053CEB9093B" captionStart="Figure 1" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figure 1. Mesosoma, dorsal view, mshs: mesoscutual suprahumeral sulcus; nt: notaulus A Ismarus nigritrochanter Liu, Chen &amp; Xu B Ismarus halidayi Foerster C Coptera sp." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.82.62148.figure1" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537295" pageId="0" pageNumber="139">1A</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
